a = 1; b = 3; c = 2; % m
u = 30*pi/180; % rad
v = 60*pi/180; % rad
w = 90*pi/180; % rad
 
%Matricerne opskrives
U = [cos(u) -sin(u) 0
sin(u) cos(u) 0
0 0 1];
V = [cos(v) 0 sin(v)
0 1 0
-sin(v) 0 cos(v)];
W = [cos(w) 0 -sin(w)
0 1 0
sin(w) 0 cos(w)];
 
%Vektorende opskrives
A = [0; 0; a];
B = [0; 0; b];
C = [0; 0; -c];
 
%Der udregnes hvor resultatet bliver en vektor
P = U * (V * (W * C + B) + A) %Rkkeflgen af matricerne er ikke ligegyldig

J = [-sin(u)*(b*sin(v)-c*sin(v-w)) cos(u)*(b*cos(v)-c*cos(v-w)) c*cos(v-w)*cos(u)
cos(u)*(b*sin(v)-c*sin(v-w)) sin(u)*(b*cos(v)-c*cos(v-w)) c*cos(v-w)*sin(u)
0 c*sin(v-w)-b*sin(v) -c*sin(v-w)];
 
dX = J\f;
 
X = X - dX;
 
iter = iter + 1;
 
ea = 100*max(abs(dX./X));
 
if iter>=20 || ea<=es
break
end
end

L = [250 100 300 200]*1e-3; % m Lngder af stangelementerne
A = [65 8 102 47]*1e-6; % m^2 Tvrsnitsarealer af stangelementerne
E = 210e9; % Pa E-modul for stangelementerne
k = A*E./L; % N/m Fjederkonstanter for stangelementerne
K = [ k(1) -k(1) 0 0 0 % N/m Stivhedsmatrix
-k(1) k(1)+k(2) -k(2) 0 0
0 -k(2) k(2)+k(3) -k(3) 0
0 0 -k(3) k(3)+k(4) -k(4)
0 0 0 -k(4) k(4)];
 
Kred = K(1:4,1:4);
F = 1244; %N
Fvek = [F; 0; 0; F];
